description: PC tool to monitor, configure and control some devices of Proteus Industries Inc.
releaseNotes:
============================
FluidVision Utilities v2.5.0
+ Implement diagnostic function.
+ Fix temperature display in EoL view.
+ No longer auto ask for migating data.
+ Operator no longer can edit sensor information.

============================
FluidVision Utilities v2.4.1
+ Update software information.

============================
FluidVision Utilities v2.4.0
+ Now wait for user confirmation before migrating sensor data.
+ Input data now will be validated when editing & creating new calibration profile.
+ Fix duplicated messages when a command is failed and error code is sent.

============================
FluidVision Utilities v2.3.1
+ Update some descriptions to avoid confusion.

============================
FluidVision Utilities v2.3.0
+ Automatically download missing fluid profiles from Proteus server on the first run after installation or software update.
+ On the first run after installation or software update, install required serial driver if it is missing on the running PC.
+ Supports new temperature calibration profiles which base on resistor - temperature.

============================
FluidVision Utilities v2.2.0
+ Support updating device description files (Software Setup -> Update device description files...)

============================
FluidVision Utilities v2.1.0
+ Beside downloading from Proteus server, now fluid viscosity files can also be downloaded from a network-attached storage (NAS)
+ Fluid selection is moved from Sensor Setup screen to Hub Setup screen.
+ Enhanced No Device mode: user can now configure an unconnected device and export/import the settings to/from a file so that the settings can be copied to other units.

============================
FluidVision Utilities v2.0.0
+ The software is integrated into Windows OS via software installer
+ Support over-the-air software update
+ New Software Setup page to change settings of the software
+ Fluid viscosity files can be downloaded from Proteus server
+ Support ETS EtherCAT 3-sesnor
+ New "No device mode" allows using the software while not connected with any device
title: FluidVision Utilities
